column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as SpecobjId       FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL  SELECT u.up_name as [name], s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID
